Package: twittercrawler
Type: Package
Title: Collect network data via Twitter's API.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andrew Carr
Maintainer: Andrew Carr <carr@andrewjohn@gmail.com>
Description: The Twitter API is a valuable data source for researchers, but rate limiting and the narrow uses of the API endpoints make the collection of network data cumbersome.  This package facilitates the process of collecting network data (user data tibbles and edgelists) using the Twitter API. 
License: MIT + File LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
